{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1724010,"duration_api_ms":1892888,"num_turns":20,"result":"All checks pass: 329 tests, clippy clean, fmt clean. Now producing the ExecutionPayload:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"completion_round\": 20,\n  \"cycle\": 1,\n  \"attempt\": 1,\n  \"change_summary\": \"Made run_id and plan_hash required (non-optional) parameters across the TaskRunLineagePort trait, service functions, and FS adapter. Removed all runless matching/backfill code (unique_terminal_replay_match runless guards, find_matching_running_task_run runless fallbacks, started_at-based disambiguation). Removed all snapshot auto-population code (safe_plan_hash_backfill, snapshot_plan_hash, snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation field from TaskRunEntry). This eliminates cross-adapter coupling and CorruptRecord error misuse as natural consequences. Test count dropped from 360 to 329 (31 tests removed that tested now-deleted runless/backfill/snapshot behavior).\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"amend-1\",\n      \"description\": \"Make run_id a REQUIRED parameter (&str, not Option<&str>) in record_bead_start, update_task_run, record_bead_completion, and the TaskRunLineagePort trait\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"details\": \"Changed TaskRunLineagePort::record_task_run_start run_id from Option<&str> to &str, TaskRunLineagePort::update_task_run run_id from Option<&str> to &str, record_bead_start run_id from Option<&str> to &str, record_bead_completion run_id from Option<&str> to &str, update_task_run run_id from Option<&str> to &str. Updated FsTaskRunLineageStore impl to match. Updated all test call sites from Some(\\\"run-1\\\") to \\\"run-1\\\". Added required_run_id_populates_lineage_entry test.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"amend-2\",\n      \"description\": \"Make plan_hash a REQUIRED parameter (&str) in record_bead_start and record_task_run_start\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"details\": \"Changed TaskRunLineagePort::record_task_run_start plan_hash from Option<&str> to &str. Changed record_bead_start plan_hash from Option<&str> to &str. Updated FsTaskRunLineageStore::record_task_run_start impl to accept &str. Updated all test call sites from Some(\\\"hash-abc\\\") to \\\"hash-abc\\\".\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"amend-3\",\n      \"description\": \"Remove ALL runless matching/backfill code (unique_terminal_replay_match runless guards, find_matching_running_task_run runless fallbacks, started_at-based disambiguation)\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"details\": \"In model.rs: find_matching_running_task_run changed to take run_id: &str, now matches only by exact run_id (removed runless fallback with started_at disambiguation). matching_finalized_task_runs changed to take run_id: &str, now matches only by exact run_id (removed runless fallback). Removed 6 runless matching tests. In fs.rs: unique_terminal_replay_match simplified to take run_id: &str and started_at: DateTime<Utc> (both required), removed contract violation check, return type changed from AppResult<Option<usize>> to Option<usize>. In update_task_run impl: removed entire else branch (runless path), removed runless matching arms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"amend-4\",\n      \"description\": \"Remove ALL snapshot auto-population code (safe_plan_hash_backfill, snapshot_plan_hash, snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation field)\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"details\": \"In model.rs: removed snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation field from TaskRunEntry struct, removed it from merge_attempt_entries logic. In fs.rs: removed snapshot_plan_hash function entirely, removed safe_plan_hash_backfill function entirely, removed snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation from TaskRunEntry construction in record_task_run_start, removed safe_plan_hash_backfill calls from record_task_run_start and update_task_run.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"amend-5\",\n      \"description\": \"Fix cross-adapter coupling and CorruptRecord error variant misuse (both eliminated as natural consequences of amendments 1-4)\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"details\": \"Cross-adapter coupling was caused by snapshot_plan_hash reading adapter state from service layer — eliminated by removing snapshot_plan_hash entirely (amend-4). CorruptRecord misuse was in runless fallback paths that used it for internal contract violations — eliminated by removing all runless code paths (amend-3). No separate code changes needed.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation_evidence\": {\n    \"tests\": \"329 passed, 0 failed, 0 ignored (down from 360 — 31 runless/backfill/snapshot tests removed)\",\n    \"clippy\": \"cargo clippy -- -D warnings: clean (no warnings or errors)\",\n    \"fmt\": \"cargo fmt --check: clean (no formatting issues)\",\n    \"files_modified\": [\n      \"src/contexts/milestone_record/service.rs\",\n      \"src/contexts/milestone_record/model.rs\",\n      \"src/adapters/fs.rs\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"outstanding_risks\": []\n}\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"dc6aa508-19dd-4e12-bdf9-726d7fd9c018","total_cost_usd":12.865718400000008,"usage":{"input_tokens":1415,"cache_creation_input_tokens":184323,"cache_read_input_tokens":851531,"output_tokens":12957,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":184323,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":311,"outputTokens":26086,"cacheReadInputTokens":2498484,"cacheCreationInputTokens":103662,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.5101668999999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":5055,"outputTokens":76465,"cacheReadInputTokens":15356978,"cacheCreationInputTokens":438426,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":12.355551500000006,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","u